    "Splunk Enterprise is an efficient data management platform that provides analysis and visualization of data [53].",
    "Splunk Enterprise Security (SES) is another solution, which is capable of correlating events for security analysis and identifying malicious and anomalous events.",
    "The free version of Splunk Enterprise known as SplunkFree is restricted to storing only up to 500 MB of data and does not contain advanced features that are available in SES.",
